- cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) is relevant as the problem involves combinatorial enumeration of subsets of points.
- cs.PR (Parallel and Distributed Computing) is mentioned in the paper as the algorithm can be parallelized on a specific parallel computing model.
- cs.SC (Symbolic Computation) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with exact fitting of points to lines, which can involve symbolic computation techniques.
